<bug>
    <id>10481</id>
    <title>Field size limit on fan page titles</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">A recent  craze  of some facebook users is to create fan pages with very long titles.</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.2">This has become an annoyance to many users and in many cases these pages are dominating the live feed pages when people like the pages.</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.3">A possible solution to this problem would be to add a character limit on the size of fan page titles_ is this possible?</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.4">I m sure many users would appreciate this fix.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
</bug>
